{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/Tools/m1-setting/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"leo-xee.io","author":"Leo-Xee","siteUrl":"https://leo-xee.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"leo-xee/blog-comments"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"leoxexe"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"e1b5e313-73d7-5736-b8ce-b9eb58943cb5","excerpt":"이 글에서는 최근에 회사에서 지급 받은 M1 Macbook Pro를 초기 세팅하면서 겪었던 병목을 다시 겪지 않고자 세팅 내용을 간단히 정리합니다. MacOS 설정   : Dark로 변경  : Pink로 변경   : 1시간으로 변경   : 25%로 변경  : Max로 변경  : 해제   -  : 100% 변경  -  : 모두 해제 (Alfred 사용)  -  : 해제   : 100% 변경   : 디스플레이 끄기 1시간으로 변경 Homebrew Homebrew…","html":"<p><img src=\"/836a847ae26446e4d939a0a4c470e983/Tools.gif\"></p>\n<p>이 글에서는 최근에 회사에서 지급 받은 M1 Macbook Pro를 초기 세팅하면서 겪었던 병목을 다시 겪지 않고자 세팅 내용을 간단히 정리합니다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"macos-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#macos-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"macos 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>MacOS 설정</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">General</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Appearance</code> : Dark로 변경</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Accent color</code> : Pink로 변경</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Desktop &amp; Screen Saver</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Show screen saver after</code> : 1시간으로 변경</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Dock &amp; Menu Bar</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Size</code> : 25%로 변경</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Magnification</code> : Max로 변경</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Show recent applications in Dock</code> : 해제</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Keyboard</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Keyboard</code> - <code class=\"language-text\">Key Repeat</code> : 100% 변경</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Shorcuts</code> - <code class=\"language-text\">Spotlight</code> : 모두 해제 (Alfred 사용)</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Input Sources</code> - <code class=\"language-text\">Caps Lock key to switch to and from ABC</code> : 해제</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Trackpad</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Tracking speed</code> : 100% 변경</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Battery</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Power Adapter</code> : 디스플레이 끄기 1시간으로 변경</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</br>\n<h1 id=\"homebrew\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#homebrew\" aria-label=\"homebrew permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Homebrew</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://brew.sh/index_ko\">Homebrew</a>는 패키지들을 쉽게 관리할 수 있도록 도와주는 Mac용 패키지 매니저이다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>설치</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ /bin/bash <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-c</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token function\">curl</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-fsSL</span> https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/HEAD/install.sh<span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>\"</span></code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<h1 id=\"iterm2\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#iterm2\" aria-label=\"iterm2 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Iterm2</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://iterm2.com/\">Iterm2</a> 는 MacOS에서 기본으로 제공하는 터미널보다 훨씬 많은 기능을 제공하는 터미널 애플리케이션이다. 여기에서는 Iterm2에 Dracula 테마를 적용할 예정이다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"설치-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98-1\" aria-label=\"설치 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>설치</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> iterm2</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"로제타-전용으로-복제-필요-시\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9C%ED%83%80-%EC%A0%84%EC%9A%A9%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EB%B3%B5%EC%A0%9C-%ED%95%84%EC%9A%94-%EC%8B%9C\" aria-label=\"로제타 전용으로 복제 필요 시 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>로제타 전용으로 복제 (필요 시)</h2>\n<p>Iterm2가 M1에 완전하게 호환되지 않는 경우를 대비해서 Iterm2를 복제해서 로제타로 실행해서 사용한다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Finder</code> - <code class=\"language-text\">Applications</code> 에서 Iterm을 우클릭 후에 <code class=\"language-text\">Duplicate</code>한다.</li>\n<li>복제한 Iterm의 이름을 Iterm Rosetta로 변경한다.</li>\n<li>Iterm Rosetta를 우클릭 후에 <code class=\"language-text\">Get info</code> 한다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Open using Rosetta</code> 를 체크한다.</li>\n<li>Iterm Rosetta를 메인으로 사용한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"테마-적용\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%85%8C%EB%A7%88-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9\" aria-label=\"테마 적용 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>테마 적용</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Dracula 테마 프리셋을 다음 명령어로 다운로드한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">git</span> clone https://github.com/dracula/iterm.git</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>다운 받은 <code class=\"language-text\">Dracula.itermcolors</code> 을 실행해서 <code class=\"language-text\">import</code> 한다.</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Preference</code> - <code class=\"language-text\">Profile</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Colors</code> 에서 <code class=\"language-text\">Color Presets</code> 를 Dracula로 변경</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Window</code> 에서 <code class=\"language-text\">Blur</code> 체크 후 25로 변경하고 <code class=\"language-text\">Transparency</code> 를 30으로 변경</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"폰트-적용\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8F%B0%ED%8A%B8-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9\" aria-label=\"폰트 적용 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>폰트 적용</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Fira Code 폰트를 <a href=\"https://github.com/tonsky/FiraCode\">GitHub 페이지</a>에서 다운로드한다.</li>\n<li>다운 받은 Fira Code를 설치한다.</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Preference</code> - <code class=\"language-text\">Profile</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Text</code>에서 <code class=\"language-text\">Font</code>를 Fira Code로 변경</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"oh-my-zsh\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#oh-my-zsh\" aria-label=\"oh my zsh permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Oh My Zsh</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://ohmyz.sh/\">Oh My Zsh</a>는 Zsh를 쉽게 관리해주는 커뮤니티 기반 프레임워크이다. 이를 사용하면 다양한 플러그인과 테마를 사용할 수 있다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"설치-2\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98-2\" aria-label=\"설치 2 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>설치</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Oh My Zsh</code>를 다음 명령어로 설치한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">sh</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-c</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token function\">curl</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-fsSL</span> https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/master/tools/install.sh<span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"플러그인-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%94%8C%EB%9F%AC%EA%B7%B8%EC%9D%B8-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"플러그인 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>플러그인 설치</h2>\n<h3 id=\"autojump\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#autojump\" aria-label=\"autojump permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>autojump</h3>\n<p>autojump 플러그인을 다음 명령어로 설치한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> autojump</code></pre></div>\n<p>설치 후에 <code class=\"language-text\">~/.zshrc</code>의 plugins에 autojump를 추가한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token assign-left variable\">plugins</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>git autojump<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"zsh-syntax-highlighting\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#zsh-syntax-highlighting\" aria-label=\"zsh syntax highlighting permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>zsh-syntax-highlighting</h3>\n<p>syntax-highlighting 플러그인을 다음 명령어로 설치한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> zsh-syntax-highlighting</code></pre></div>\n<p>설치 후에 <code class=\"language-text\">~/.zshrc</code>의 최하단에 다음 코드를 추가한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">source</span> /usr/local/share/zsh-syntax-highlighting/zsh-syntax-highlighting.zsh</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"zsh-autosuggestions\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#zsh-autosuggestions\" aria-label=\"zsh autosuggestions permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>zsh-autosuggestions</h3>\n<p>zsh-autosuggestions 플러그인을 다음 명령어로 설치한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> zsh-autosuggestions</code></pre></div>\n<p>설치 후에 <code class=\"language-text\">~/.zshrc</code>의 최하단에 다음 코드를 추가한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">source</span> /usr/local/share/zsh-autosuggestions/zsh-autosuggestions.zsh</code></pre></div>\n</br>\n<h1 id=\"karabiner\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#karabiner\" aria-label=\"karabiner permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Karabiner</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://karabiner-elements.pqrs.org/\">Karabiner</a>는 손쉽게 키 맵핑을 커스터마이징할 수 있는 애플리케이션이다. <a href=\"https://ke-complex-modifications.pqrs.org/\">커뮤니티</a>에서 제공하는 프리셋을 사용해서 쉽게 원하는 조합으로 쉽게 세팅할 수 있다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"설치-3\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98-3\" aria-label=\"설치 3 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>설치</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> karabiner-elements</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"세팅\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%84%B8%ED%8C%85\" aria-label=\"세팅 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>세팅</h2>\n<p>저는 Vim을 사용하기 때문에 다음과 같은 프리셋과 설정을 사용한다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">CAPS_LOCK to Hyper/Escape &amp; Hyper + VIM Navigation keys</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Vimode with smart caps</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">For Korean</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">For Korean PC Keyboard</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">F4</code> 를 <code class=\"language-text\">Launchpad</code> 로 변경</li>\n</ul>\n</br>\n<h1 id=\"주요-패키지들\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A3%BC%EC%9A%94-%ED%8C%A8%ED%82%A4%EC%A7%80%EB%93%A4\" aria-label=\"주요 패키지들 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>주요 패키지들</h1>\n<h2 id=\"node\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#node\" aria-label=\"node permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Node</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 설치</span>\n$ brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> <span class=\"token function\">node</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 버전 확인</span>\n$ <span class=\"token function\">node</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-v</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"yarn\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#yarn\" aria-label=\"yarn permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Yarn</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 설치 (이미 설치한 node 제외 옵션)</span>\n$ brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> <span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> --ignore-dependencies\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 버전 확인</span>\n$ <span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-v</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"nvm\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#nvm\" aria-label=\"nvm permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>NVM</h2>\n<p>NVM을 다음 명령어로 설치한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> nvm</code></pre></div>\n<p>NVM을 위한 디렉토리를 생성한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">mkdir</span> ~/.nvm</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">~/.zshrc</code> 의 최하단에 다음 코드를 추가한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">NVM_DIR</span><span class=\"token operator\">=~</span>/.nvm\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">source</span> <span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span>brew <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--prefix</span> nvm<span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>/nvm.sh</code></pre></div>\n<p>정상적으로 설치 되었는지 확인한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ nvm <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-version</span></code></pre></div>\n<br/>\n<h1 id=\"주요-애플리케이션들\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A3%BC%EC%9A%94-%EC%95%A0%ED%94%8C%EB%A6%AC%EC%BC%80%EC%9D%B4%EC%85%98%EB%93%A4\" aria-label=\"주요 애플리케이션들 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>주요 애플리케이션들</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>필요한 애플리케이션<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>다음은 주로 사용하는 애플리케이션 목록이다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>visual-studio-code</li>\n<li>alfred</li>\n<li>chrome</li>\n<li>firefox</li>\n<li>notion</li>\n<li>figma</li>\n<li>sourcetree</li>\n<li>slack</li>\n<li>obsidian</li>\n<li>app cleaner</li>\n<li>spectacle</li>\n<li>runcat</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"M1 Macbook 초기 세팅하기","date":"September 25, 2022"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Tools/m1-setting/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/PS/b16968/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[백준/JS] 16968번 - 차량 번호판 1"}},"next":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["2486386679","3128451518"]}